  <Docs>
    <summary>Specifies options for creating an XPS document.</summary>
    <remarks><format type="text/markdown"><![CDATA[
## Remarks

`SKDocumentXpsOptions` specifies options used when creating an XPS document via <xref:SkiaSharp.SKDocument.CreateXps(SkiaSharp.SKWStream,SkiaSharp.SKDocumentXpsOptions)>.

XPS documents are only supported on Windows. On other platforms, `CreateXps` will return `null` regardless of the options provided.

## Examples

```csharp
var options = new SKDocumentXpsOptions
{
    Dpi = 300f,
    AllowNoPngs = false
};

using var stream = new SKFileWStream("output.xps");
using var doc = SKDocument.CreateXps(stream, options);
using var canvas = doc.BeginPage(595, 842);
// draw content
doc.EndPage();
doc.Close();
```
]]></format></remarks>
